data.description: Welcome Home to this Beautiful well maintained 3 BR / 2.5 BA home offered by the Original Owner. Recent updates include wood flooring on the main, granite Kitchen counters, new HVAC with digital wi-fi thermostat, and wi-fi connected garage door opener. The front covered porch greets your guests and the beautiful wood floors and arched doorways lead them into the Foyer though to the Living Room with its cozy stone fireplace. Enjoy preparing meals in this Open Kitchen with stained cabinets, granite counters, tile backsplash, and a view into the Living Room. Dine at the breakfast bar, Breakfast Area or your open Dining Room. Carpeted stairs lead up to a spacious loft which can be used as entertainment, study, or office space. Your Owner's Suite includes great windows and a trey ceiling, and your private Bath has a separate shower and garden tub, separate vanities, and a walk-in closet. Two additional Bedrooms, a Hall Bath, and Laundry Room complete the upper floor. Relax, cookout or entertain on the private rear patio.  Great Location near shopping, schools, GA Gwinnett College, downtown, entertainment, and parks. Low HOA and no rental restrictions.  Refrigerator and w/d stays.
